# Live Coding the intersection between the Arts, Technology and Research
## Sam Aaron

* Learning
    * If the lesson is meaningful the student is more likely to be engaged.
    * A large part of a lesson is behaviour management and evaluation, very little is actual teaching.
    * With SonicPi you need to go from no code to a functioning program very quickly
* Architecture
    * Constraint: teachable to 10-yr-old children
    * Create systems like this: complex internals, simplistic interface
    * A simple system has huge benefits

* Read: Structure and Interpretation of Computer Program
